channel.description:
Hello,
I was just on my way to code a server and client that will hopefully release to be giant! Well then I thought ,"Why shouldn't i make a dev. team so that the server and client will be twice as good!?" So I did.
[b]How to apply?[/b] Very Simple really fill out the form bellow then i will PM you the link to the forums we are using. Well some basic information on the site is that it is Scape Help. Owned by frell. He is letting me have my own board with child boards to host my dev. team.
Format for applying [code] Name: Age: Msn: Coding XP: Proof: Position Wanted: [/code]
[b]Note I will NOT accept people without XP and/or no proof.
[center][b]~Members~[/b][/center]
Coders:
[ul][li]Got Java?[/li] [li]Yz85Racer[/li] [li]Newb 2341[/li] [li]Sick of Air[/li] [li]ricky james[/li] [li]Unlimited Open![/li][/ul]
Frell didnt want everyone thinking i was advertising as you could tell: [IMG]http://i12.tinypic.com/6446p2s.jpg[/img]
